name: X-Ray
desc: Dental X-rays are images of your teeth that your dentist uses to evaluate your oral health.

name: Dental Cleanings
desc: There are three types of dental cleanings: prophylaxis cleaning,root planing and gross debridement.

name: Root Canals
desc: Root canal treatment is a dental procedure used to treat infection at the centre of a tooth.

name: Implants
desc: Dental implants are replacement tooth roots.

name: Orthodontics
desc: Orthodontics is a dentistry specialty that addresses the diagnosis, prevention, management.

name: Whitening
desc: Teeth whitening involves bleaching your teeth to make them lighter.
